  "title": "Human Resource Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p><ul><li>Perform bi-monthly and monthly payroll processing (2 runs) using Whyze HR system for approximately 450 headcounts</li><li>Verify expenses, claims, allowances, overtime.</li><li>Preparation of monthly payroll and headcount reconciliations & variance analysis</li><li>Ensure timely and accurate submissions of payroll, CP, clearance of Income tax, IR21</li><li>Prepare payroll reports</li><li>Handle work pass application, renewal and etc</li><li>Application of Training courses</li><li>Handle General Administration duties</li><li>Assist in receruitment related duties when needed</li></ul><p><strong>Qualification</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Human Resource Management</li><li>Min 2 - 5 years of relevant experience</li><li>Familiar with Whyze HR Solution system</li><li>Experience in construction industry will be an added advantage</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
